The modules in backend are:

```
src/cli         CLI scripts
src/api         FastAPI server
src/loader      Dataset loader and shared model definitions
src/es          Provide full text search over the dataset, using ElasticSearch
src/duckdb      Provide Relational and Graph DB queries over the dataset
```